We use the values in Table 13.8 for the observed values and the corresponding expected values.

$$
\\begin{aligned}
L\chi^2 &= 2\Big[42 \times \ln\Big(\frac{42}{37.77}\Big)  + 154 \times \ln\Big(\frac{154}{158.23}\Big)\dots \\\\
